    question: "Can I change my insurance provider after enrollment?",
    answer: "Yes, you can change health insurance providers annually with proper notice (usually by November 30th for changes effective January 1st). For other insurance types, change options vary by policy terms. We help you evaluate switching opportunities and manage the transition process."
